dnsmasq

This is the dnsmasq module. It installs, runs, and configures dnsmasq.

Usage
--------

To use this module:

    class {'dnsmasq':
        domains => ['google.com', 'onyxpoint.com']
    }

Where domains is a list of domains that you would like to redirect to 1.2.3.4

This module will only work as expected if you are the machine it is enabled on as the primary nameserver